WEBVTT

00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:23.800 line:80%
They're so beautiful, so unique.

00:00:32.270 --> 00:00:34.550 line:80%
There's hot water in the kettle
for you to wash up.

00:00:34.550 --> 00:00:35.590 line:80%
It's getting late.

00:00:35.590 --> 00:00:36.800 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, you should

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.130 line:80%
get some rest early.

00:00:38.550 --> 00:00:39.680 line:80%
Thank you, Fuling.

00:00:45.190 --> 00:00:46.190 line:80%
What do you think?

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:49.720 line:80%
It's pretty good.

00:01:00.590 --> 00:01:04.360 line:80%
This must be the surprise
Qianqian mentioned.

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:20.480 line:80%
The hot water is on the table.

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:21.310 line:80%
Wash up first.

00:01:29.950 --> 00:01:30.620 line:80%
Okay.

00:02:42.110 --> 00:02:42.830 line:80%
Hold on.

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:44.760 line:80%
Just pour it in here.

00:02:44.879 --> 00:02:47.740 line:80%
The water in the basin
has already gone cold anyway.

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:00.620 line:80%
Just pour it in?

00:03:24.670 --> 00:03:26.530 line:80%
You don't like soaking your feet?

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:36.270 line:80%
I...

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:38.360 line:80%
I don't know what you're used to,

00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:39.920 line:80%
but in my family,

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.110 line:80%
we all soak in the same basin.

00:03:45.990 --> 00:03:46.879 line:80%
Or I can

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.800 line:80%
ask Fuling to boil another kettle
of hot water for you later.

00:03:49.800 --> 00:03:50.430 line:80%
No need.

00:03:50.950 --> 00:03:52.280 line:80%
That's not what I meant.

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:57.550 line:80%
I'll just go outside
and rinse with cold water in a bit.

00:03:57.550 --> 00:03:58.360 line:80%
Cold water?

00:03:58.990 --> 00:04:01.510 line:80%
In weather this cold,
washing with cold water—

00:04:01.510 --> 00:04:02.830 line:80%
you'll catch a chill.

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:04.510 line:80%
I'm used to it.

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:25.190 line:80%
There's only one bed here.

00:04:29.070 --> 00:04:30.600 line:80%
You and Changning rest first.

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:32.400 line:80%
I'll go stay outside for a while.

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:38.480 line:80%
You can't stay outside all night, can you?

00:04:39.430 --> 00:04:40.670 line:80%
Fuling said

00:04:40.990 --> 00:04:42.870 line:80%
this is the only guest room left.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:44.750 line:80%
It's alright.

00:04:47.140 --> 00:04:49.520 line:80%
I'll ask the staff here
at Yixiang Restaurant

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.920 line:80%
if I can share a room with them
for the night.

00:05:03.750 --> 00:05:04.880 line:80%
I'm going out first.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.430 line:80%
What went wrong?

00:05:27.850 --> 00:05:30.180 line:80%
Did the ambush with the sack
scare him off?

00:05:31.910 --> 00:05:33.840 line:80%
Or did the foot-soaking scare him?

00:05:34.730 --> 00:05:37.060 line:80%
Is soaking feet really that frightening?

00:07:05.420 --> 00:07:10.650 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:07:10.670 --> 00:07:13.370 line:80%
[Episode 15]

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:39.480 line:80%
Mr. Yan, it's late.

00:07:39.480 --> 00:07:42.080 line:80%
Why haven't you gone back
to your room to sleep?

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:43.430 line:80%
She has her little sister with her,

00:07:43.430 --> 00:07:44.690 line:80%
so it's inconvenient.

00:07:46.550 --> 00:07:48.230 line:80%
I hadn't thought of that.

00:07:48.990 --> 00:07:51.310 line:80%
The staff here share rooms, two per room.

00:07:51.670 --> 00:07:54.520 line:80%
But one of them snores terribly loudly,

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:56.800 line:80%
so no one can sleep well beside him.

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.990 line:80%
If you don't mind,

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.400 line:80%
you may rest in his room tonight.

00:08:02.310 --> 00:08:03.190 line:80%
I don't mind.

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:38.000 line:80%
Don't tell me

00:08:38.349 --> 00:08:41.150 line:80%
you really don't plan to
take the sisters with you?

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:44.040 line:80%
Once you leave,
it'll be hard to see them again.

00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:46.740 line:80%
How can I take them with me?

00:08:48.040 --> 00:08:50.760 line:80%
Take them to the front lines
to endure hardships,

00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:52.950 line:80%
with their lives on the line every moment?

00:08:52.950 --> 00:08:56.120 line:80%
Precisely because the battlefield
is fraught with peril,

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:58.040 line:80%
you need a woman
who can shoulder the responsibility

00:08:58.040 --> 00:09:00.170 line:80%
of being the matriarch of your family.

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:01.920 line:80%
In my view,

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:04.520 line:80%
she's no fragile woman.

00:09:30.470 --> 00:09:31.470 line:80%
She's wonderful.

00:09:32.550 --> 00:09:36.010 line:80%
She is resilient, more so than
many women from noble families.

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:37.830 line:80%
But I only want to see her

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:41.400 line:80%
grow wild and free,
like grass in an open field.

00:09:42.920 --> 00:09:46.970 line:80%
The role of matriarch
would only confine her.

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:18.710 line:80%
Wake up.

00:10:19.070 --> 00:10:19.710 line:80%
Wake up!

00:10:25.310 --> 00:10:26.040 line:80%
Scholar Song?

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:27.100 line:80%
Quick, help him up!

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:28.950 line:80%
Easy, easy.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.200 line:80%
Scholar Song,

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:32.640 line:80%
you're covered in wounds.

00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:34.470 line:80%
W-Were you robbed?

00:10:35.950 --> 00:10:36.590 line:80%
One...

00:10:37.670 --> 00:10:38.470 line:80%
Two...

00:10:39.880 --> 00:10:40.760 line:80%
Three...

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:43.080 line:80%
-Four...
-L-Last night...

00:10:44.430 --> 00:10:45.640 line:80%
Five...

00:10:47.190 --> 00:10:49.520 line:80%
-Six...
-I think I was beaten up by a child.

00:11:17.190 --> 00:11:19.250 line:80%
You didn't stay up all night, did you?

00:11:24.520 --> 00:11:25.550 line:80%
I told you last night.

00:11:25.550 --> 00:11:27.430 line:80%
That attendant in the dormitory
snores terribly.

00:11:27.430 --> 00:11:29.640 line:80%
You must've been kept awake by the noise.

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:31.470 line:80%
How about I go get you some tea?

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:38.270 line:80%
Go get some sleep.

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:42.000 line:80%
The staff at Yixiang Restaurant
are looking after Changning.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.070 line:80%
Don't tell me

00:11:43.400 --> 00:11:46.200 line:80%
you really don't plan to
take the sisters with you?

00:11:47.190 --> 00:11:48.400 line:80%
Once you leave,

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:50.440 line:80%
it'll be hard to see them again.

00:11:53.190 --> 00:11:54.890 line:80%
Are you listening?

00:11:57.280 --> 00:11:58.070 line:80%
Go on.

00:11:58.920 --> 00:12:00.520 line:80%
What are you thinking about?

00:12:01.430 --> 00:12:02.190 line:80%
Nothing.

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.310 line:80%
I just woke up,

00:12:04.310 --> 00:12:05.520 line:80%
so I'm a bit out of it.

00:12:06.470 --> 00:12:07.670 line:80%
What did you just say?

00:12:07.760 --> 00:12:08.550 line:80%
I said

00:12:08.550 --> 00:12:11.520 line:80%
the staff at Yixiang Restaurant
are looking after Changning.

00:12:11.520 --> 00:12:13.550 line:80%
I can manage
the braised meat shop by myself.

00:12:13.550 --> 00:12:14.240 line:80%
It's okay.

00:12:14.430 --> 00:12:15.510 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:12:15.830 --> 00:12:17.600 line:80%
I need to buy something
at the bookshop anyway.

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:18.400 line:80%
Fatty Celery!

00:12:36.640 --> 00:12:38.290 line:80%
Mr. Yan, Mrs. Fan,

00:12:38.640 --> 00:12:40.040 line:80%
sorry about that, sorry.

00:12:40.710 --> 00:12:42.640 line:80%
Not that way. This way!

00:12:43.350 --> 00:12:44.470 line:80%
Instant karma...

00:12:49.950 --> 00:12:50.680 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:53.800 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:00.900 line:80%
[Noodles]

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:14.120 line:80%
You have no appetite?

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:16.280 line:80%
You seem out of sorts too.

00:13:16.470 --> 00:13:18.870 line:80%
Did the bookshop owner
give you a hard time?

00:13:20.030 --> 00:13:20.630 line:80%
No.

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:26.400 line:80%
Waiter, bill.

00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:27.190 line:80%
Coming.

00:13:27.010 --> 00:13:30.310 line:80%
[Noodles]

00:13:27.640 --> 00:13:28.430 line:80%
Sir,

00:13:28.430 --> 00:13:30.160 line:80%
that will be 30 wen.

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:31.420 line:80%
I'll get it.

00:13:31.710 --> 00:13:32.400 line:80%
Okay.

00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:35.120 line:80%
A grown man out to eat with a woman,

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:36.430 line:80%
and he lets her pay?

00:13:36.950 --> 00:13:38.550 line:80%
Isn't he ashamed of himself?

00:13:41.470 --> 00:13:43.830 line:80%
Could he be a kept man?

00:13:45.950 --> 00:13:47.310 line:80%
I know that guy.

00:13:47.550 --> 00:13:48.920 line:80%
He's the An family's matrilocal husband—

00:13:48.920 --> 00:13:50.120 line:80%
he lives off his wife.

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:52.240 line:80%
Heaven knows what the An family's daughter

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:53.770 line:80%
sees in that spineless man.

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:56.200 line:80%
Just his pretty face, I suppose.

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:01.000 line:80%
Are you full?

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:04.430 line:80%
Waiter, bill!

00:14:04.100 --> 00:14:07.460 line:80%
[Noodles]

00:14:04.430 --> 00:14:05.120 line:80%
Coming.

00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:09.190 line:80%
That will be 21 wen.

00:14:09.310 --> 00:14:09.950 line:80%
Just

00:14:10.120 --> 00:14:11.160 line:80%
make it 20 wen.

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:29.310 line:80%
Could he be a kept man as well?

00:14:29.520 --> 00:14:32.270 line:80%
With looks like that,
he's certainly cut out for it.

00:14:32.270 --> 00:14:32.950 line:80%
Yeah.

00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:38.040 line:80%
Did you buy too many things for Changning?

00:14:39.240 --> 00:14:41.140 line:80%
No, it's just that I...

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:41.950 line:80%
I bet

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:43.760 line:80%
he saw the An family's matrilocal husband
embarrass himself

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.290 line:80%
and was trying to save face.

00:14:52.950 --> 00:14:54.350 line:80%
The money's underneath.

00:14:58.950 --> 00:14:59.590 line:80%
No need.

00:15:00.310 --> 00:15:02.240 line:80%
I'm afraid they won't have change.

00:15:06.470 --> 00:15:09.160 line:80%
Your New Year's gift. Open it.

00:15:11.710 --> 00:15:13.240 line:80%
Money is of no use to me.

00:15:15.830 --> 00:15:17.120 line:80%
You're not taking it with you?

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:17.670 line:80%
Wait...

00:15:29.040 --> 00:15:29.770 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:15:30.550 --> 00:15:32.010 line:80%
This isn't like you at all.

00:15:32.550 --> 00:15:33.950 line:80%
Having a wife really does change a man.

00:15:33.950 --> 00:15:35.040 line:80%
Why do you have so much to say?

00:15:35.040 --> 00:15:36.040 line:80%
Here, here, here.

00:15:36.670 --> 00:15:38.420 line:80%
Sir, you must be joking.

00:15:38.520 --> 00:15:40.670 line:80%
We're just a small shop.
Such a large silver ingot…

00:15:40.670 --> 00:15:41.520 line:80%
We really

00:15:41.520 --> 00:15:42.400 line:80%
can't break it.

00:15:43.350 --> 00:15:44.070 line:80%
I... I...

00:15:44.590 --> 00:15:45.740 line:80%
I have some loose coins.

00:15:45.740 --> 00:15:46.470 line:80%
That's good.

00:15:46.470 --> 00:15:47.520 line:80%
Let me pay with the coins.

00:15:47.520 --> 00:15:49.120 line:80%
Alright, please come again.

00:15:49.430 --> 00:15:50.580 line:80%
Then take this.

00:15:54.070 --> 00:15:55.280 line:80%
Look at this young gentleman,

00:15:55.280 --> 00:15:56.310 line:80%
so young...

00:15:57.280 --> 00:15:58.800 line:80%
Then I'll keep it for you.

00:15:58.800 --> 00:15:59.660 line:80%
Maybe

00:15:59.710 --> 00:16:01.370 line:80%
he's some noble young master,

00:16:01.520 --> 00:16:02.760 line:80%
coming to our area

00:16:02.760 --> 00:16:04.520 line:80%
to observe the lives of common folks.

00:16:04.520 --> 00:16:05.670 line:80%
Yes, exactly.

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:12.160 line:80%
Who would carry a whole silver ingot
just to pay for a meal?

00:16:12.160 --> 00:16:14.240 line:80%
Where did you get so much money?

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:18.640 line:80%
Don't tell me the bookshop owner
gave it to you again.

00:16:18.640 --> 00:16:19.880 line:80%
Just keep it.

00:16:20.850 --> 00:16:24.450 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:16:37.520 --> 00:16:38.950 line:80%
You're finally back.

00:16:38.950 --> 00:16:40.350 line:80%
Something terrible has happened!

00:16:40.350 --> 00:16:41.210 line:80%
What happened?

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:44.520 line:80%
The county office
suddenly requisitioned grain.

00:16:44.520 --> 00:16:45.580 line:80%
Not only grain—

00:16:45.610 --> 00:16:46.880 line:80%
they want money too.

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:48.550 line:80%
They're levying it per person—

00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:50.280 line:80%
four taels each.

00:16:50.280 --> 00:16:51.190 line:80%
That much?

00:16:51.880 --> 00:16:53.160 line:80%
Isn't that daylight robbery?

00:16:53.160 --> 00:16:53.830 line:80%
Exactly!

00:16:53.830 --> 00:16:55.490 line:80%
Our family can barely manage,

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:57.920 line:80%
but those landless hired hands
and tenant farmers—

00:16:57.920 --> 00:16:59.400 line:80%
they have neither money nor grain.

00:16:59.400 --> 00:17:00.590 line:80%
And the New Year festival just passed.

00:17:00.590 --> 00:17:02.280 line:80%
What are they supposed to do?

00:17:02.950 --> 00:17:05.070 line:80%
-Yeah, we can't survive this.
-What are we supposed to do?

00:17:05.070 --> 00:17:05.909 line:80%
I also heard people

00:17:05.909 --> 00:17:08.960 line:80%
from the neighboring village went to kneel
at the county office to beg for mercy.

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:09.869 line:80%
They knelt all day

00:17:09.869 --> 00:17:12.240 line:80%
but didn't even get to see the Magistrate.

00:17:13.909 --> 00:17:15.550 line:80%
Our family can manage to pay

00:17:15.550 --> 00:17:16.950 line:80%
some taels of silver now.

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:18.960 line:80%
But in Xigu Lane, there're folks

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:19.960 line:80%
who can't even scrape together one tael,

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:21.820 line:80%
even if they empty their savings.

00:17:22.040 --> 00:17:24.040 line:80%
It's just after the New Year festival;

00:17:24.040 --> 00:17:25.440 line:80%
everyone is out of money.

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:28.240 line:80%
I have to go check on my grandfather.

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.800 line:80%
Since Uncle passed away,

00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:31.530 line:80%
who will pay this money for him?

00:17:32.830 --> 00:17:34.360 line:80%
Do you need me to go with you?

00:17:35.800 --> 00:17:36.550 line:80%
No need.

00:17:37.200 --> 00:17:39.110 line:80%
I'll just sneak a look and leave.

00:17:39.110 --> 00:17:40.980 line:80%
I won't run into that woman.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:43.660 line:80%
You going would attract
too much attention.

00:17:45.440 --> 00:17:47.390 line:80%
Well, why would the county office

00:17:47.390 --> 00:17:49.120 line:80%
suddenly demand so much money?

00:17:51.280 --> 00:17:53.390 line:80%
When the government requisitions grain,

00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:55.390 line:80%
all county offices
in the Jizhou Prefecture

00:17:55.390 --> 00:17:57.520 line:80%
receive the same official documents.

00:17:57.520 --> 00:17:59.520 line:80%
Requisitioning both grain and money
like this—

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:01.180 line:80%
it's practically unheard of.

00:18:01.390 --> 00:18:03.920 line:80%
Unless other counties are doing the same,

00:18:04.240 --> 00:18:07.070 line:80%
it's possible the Magistrate here
is taking the chance

00:18:07.070 --> 00:18:08.400 line:80%
to line his own pockets.

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:11.340 line:80%
That's enough.

00:18:16.870 --> 00:18:17.470 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:18:22.910 --> 00:18:25.350 line:80%
Slip the money quietly
into Mrs. Zhao's house.

00:18:25.350 --> 00:18:26.480 line:80%
The New Year just passed.

00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:28.210 line:80%
Everyone's pockets are empty.

00:18:28.350 --> 00:18:30.080 line:80%
Don't let the old couple worry.

00:18:31.070 --> 00:18:31.600 line:80%
Okay.

00:18:40.520 --> 00:18:43.000 line:80%
Requisitioning both grain and money...

00:18:43.520 --> 00:18:45.630 line:80%
They're pushing us into a dead end!

00:18:47.680 --> 00:18:49.110 line:80%
Some old wretches

00:18:49.480 --> 00:18:52.150 line:80%
can't carry anything or do any work,

00:18:52.680 --> 00:18:54.960 line:80%
yet they hole up in their rooms

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:56.070 line:80%
all day,

00:18:56.070 --> 00:18:58.000 line:80%
eating and drinking at others' expense!

00:18:58.000 --> 00:19:00.200 line:80%
They're just a burden to everyone!

00:19:03.200 --> 00:19:04.480 line:80%
As the saying goes,

00:19:04.870 --> 00:19:07.800 line:80%
"An old man who won't die is a thief."

00:19:24.630 --> 00:19:25.430 line:80%
Grandfather.

00:19:27.720 --> 00:19:28.550 line:80%
Grandfather!

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:30.630 line:80%
Get up!

00:19:36.150 --> 00:19:37.910 line:80%
Are you all right, Grandfather?

00:19:37.910 --> 00:19:40.390 line:80%
Changyu, what are you doing here?

00:19:40.910 --> 00:19:43.310 line:80%
Go. Go, quickly.

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:46.590 line:80%
I'm just a useless old man.

00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:51.310 line:80%
I've brought this suffering on myself.

00:19:55.730 --> 00:19:58.300 line:80%
Your son is dead, yet you still sponge off
your daughter-in-law!

00:19:58.300 --> 00:19:59.630 line:80%
You shameless old fool!

00:20:02.590 --> 00:20:03.960 line:80%
You wretched old thing,

00:20:04.550 --> 00:20:06.680 line:80%
I'll kick you out sooner or later!

00:20:10.910 --> 00:20:12.240 line:80%
You jinx!

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:21.290 line:80%
Grandfather can't even get a sip of water,

00:20:21.310 --> 00:20:23.390 line:80%
yet... yet you sit here eating meat!

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:24.110 line:80%
You...

00:20:24.590 --> 00:20:25.630 line:80%
Get out of here!

00:20:25.830 --> 00:20:26.760 line:80%
Pah!

00:20:27.870 --> 00:20:29.250 line:80%
This house is mine!

00:20:29.720 --> 00:20:31.480 line:80%
Get the hell out immediately!

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:33.820 line:80%
Back then, you and your husband said,

00:20:34.110 --> 00:20:35.720 line:80%
"If there are no males in the family,

00:20:35.720 --> 00:20:37.800 line:80%
the property goes to
the nearest male kin."

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:39.040 line:80%
Your husband is dead now.

00:20:39.040 --> 00:20:40.760 line:80%
What gives you the right
to occupy this house?

00:20:40.760 --> 00:20:43.000 line:80%
My eldest daughter can bring in a husband!

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:44.930 line:80%
The Legal Code of Great Yin states,

00:20:45.070 --> 00:20:46.680 line:80%
"If a wife is unfilial
after her husband's death,

00:20:46.680 --> 00:20:49.760 line:80%
the father-in-law can repudiate her
in his son's name!"

00:20:49.760 --> 00:20:51.000 line:80%
You jinx,

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:52.350 line:80%
you're full of crap!

00:20:54.680 --> 00:20:55.680 line:80%
Fan Changyu,

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:57.960 line:80%
bullying your elders
will land you in prison!

00:20:57.960 --> 00:20:59.310 line:80%
Dad! Dad!

00:20:59.310 --> 00:21:02.110 line:80%
Fan Changyu slapped
your eldest daughter-in-law, Dad!

00:21:02.110 --> 00:21:03.910 line:80%
Fan Changyu slapped me!

00:21:05.480 --> 00:21:07.090 line:80%
Open your darn eyes and look.

00:21:06.820 --> 00:21:11.910 line:80%
[Buyer: Fan Erniu]

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:10.680 line:80%
The name on this title deed
is my father's.

00:21:12.350 --> 00:21:13.810 line:80%
Grandfather can testify.

00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:16.440 line:80%
What is this?

00:21:17.040 --> 00:21:18.170 line:80%
This is impossible.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:21.040 line:80%
I can throw you out of this house
whenever I please!

00:21:29.280 --> 00:21:31.680 line:80%
Changyu, I'm begging you!

00:21:32.070 --> 00:21:35.070 line:80%
Please don't kick us out!
I'm just a widow with children!

00:21:35.070 --> 00:21:37.870 line:80%
Your uncle's mourning period
isn't even over yet!

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:41.780 line:80%
-Please, Changyu!
-My parents' mourning period wasn't over

00:21:41.810 --> 00:21:44.010 line:80%
at that time either, and what did you do?

00:21:46.150 --> 00:21:47.280 line:80%
Get out.

00:21:59.550 --> 00:22:00.350 line:80%
Grandfather,

00:22:00.830 --> 00:22:03.520 line:80%
keep the title deed with you.
Put it away safely.

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:07.330 line:80%
Whether to kick the whole lot of them out,

00:22:07.680 --> 00:22:08.910 line:80%
you decide.

00:22:11.110 --> 00:22:12.350 line:80%
Changyu,

00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:15.680 line:80%
you're just like your father—

00:22:16.960 --> 00:22:19.550 line:80%
good and kindhearted.

00:22:22.630 --> 00:22:24.800 line:80%
Just go. Leave me.

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:27.630 line:80%
Life and death are fated.

00:22:28.150 --> 00:22:29.350 line:80%
What fate?

00:22:29.480 --> 00:22:30.590 line:80%
I don't believe in fate.

00:22:30.590 --> 00:22:32.760 line:80%
-Come with me. Let's go home.
-Go!

00:22:33.150 --> 00:22:34.910 line:80%
Even if I smash my head against this place
and die,

00:22:34.910 --> 00:22:36.440 line:80%
I won't go with you.

00:22:37.040 --> 00:22:40.040 line:80%
I don't deserve it.

00:22:40.350 --> 00:22:41.440 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.900 line:80%
What's all this talk
about deserving or not?

00:22:47.310 --> 00:22:51.440 line:80%
Your father wasn't my biological son.

00:22:52.790 --> 00:22:55.590 line:80%
It's my fault your whole family suffered.

00:22:56.800 --> 00:22:58.280 line:80%
This is my retribution.

00:22:59.830 --> 00:23:02.390 line:80%
It's all retribution.

00:23:05.720 --> 00:23:07.440 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,

00:23:08.910 --> 00:23:11.800 line:80%
your father came to Xigu Lane
with your mother.

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:14.760 line:80%
He gave me a large sum of money,

00:23:14.760 --> 00:23:18.760 line:80%
saying he had made enemies
while working as an escort

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:20.150 line:80%
and needed to lie low.

00:23:21.050 --> 00:23:24.590 line:80%
My real son, Erniu, was snatched
by human traffickers when he was little.

00:23:24.590 --> 00:23:25.850 line:80%
So he asked me

00:23:25.910 --> 00:23:29.110 line:80%
if he could register
under Fan Erniu's identity.

00:23:30.590 --> 00:23:32.690 line:80%
Then, I told outsiders

00:23:33.110 --> 00:23:35.240 line:80%
that Erniu, who had gone missing
all those years ago,

00:23:35.240 --> 00:23:37.410 line:80%
had found his way back.

00:23:38.390 --> 00:23:40.550 line:80%
The day before the incident,

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:46.550 line:80%
your father and mother came to me.

00:23:47.830 --> 00:23:50.280 line:80%
They gave me a final letter

00:23:50.550 --> 00:23:52.350 line:80%
and this title deed.

00:23:53.480 --> 00:23:54.800 line:80%
I asked

00:23:55.200 --> 00:23:58.200 line:80%
if the enemies from back then
had finally found him.

00:23:59.070 --> 00:24:01.040 line:80%
He wouldn't say anything.

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:02.390 line:80%
He just said

00:24:02.760 --> 00:24:04.520 line:80%
that only by their deaths

00:24:04.870 --> 00:24:09.150 line:80%
could they protect the lives
of you and your sister.

00:24:10.720 --> 00:24:12.200 line:80%
As you know,

00:24:12.790 --> 00:24:17.190 line:80%
Daniu had fallen into gambling
over the years.

00:24:18.240 --> 00:24:20.600 line:80%
After the incident with your parents,

00:24:20.720 --> 00:24:23.980 line:80%
he just stole that letter and burned it,

00:24:24.200 --> 00:24:27.760 line:80%
wanting to seize
all your family's property!

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:31.760 line:80%
I'm old and useless.

00:24:32.550 --> 00:24:35.830 line:80%
I couldn't control him at all.

00:24:36.960 --> 00:24:39.710 line:80%
Later, Daniu met with misfortune,

00:24:40.150 --> 00:24:41.910 line:80%
and his wife was unfilial...

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:43.590 line:80%
I believe

00:24:44.590 --> 00:24:48.630 line:80%
this is all retribution
for my selfishness.

00:24:55.520 --> 00:24:57.390 line:80%
Father and Mother already knew

00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:00.800 line:80%
their days were numbered
before they were killed.

00:25:01.550 --> 00:25:02.830 line:80%
Why did Father believe

00:25:02.830 --> 00:25:05.890 line:80%
that dying with Mother
would protect Changning and me?

00:25:05.910 --> 00:25:08.440 line:80%
But why is it different
from what Lord Li said?

00:25:09.260 --> 00:25:11.120 line:80%
What really happened?

00:25:16.550 --> 00:25:18.280 line:80%
Why are you sitting here alone?

00:25:21.350 --> 00:25:22.150 line:80%
Well,

00:25:23.130 --> 00:25:25.790 line:80%
did my parents really die
at the hands of bandits

00:25:25.800 --> 00:25:26.960 line:80%
over a treasure map?

00:25:27.630 --> 00:25:28.350 line:80%
You want to

00:25:29.310 --> 00:25:30.510 line:80%
avenge your parents?

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:32.800 line:80%
I do.

00:25:33.720 --> 00:25:35.320 line:80%
I dream about it every night.

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:38.020 line:80%
Then what if everything
the authorities said

00:25:38.020 --> 00:25:39.680 line:80%
when they closed the case was a lie—

00:25:39.680 --> 00:25:40.680 line:80%
what would you do?

00:25:41.760 --> 00:25:43.560 line:80%
Why would the authorities lie?

00:25:44.510 --> 00:25:47.880 line:80%
Just as your uncle
colluded with Advisor Guo when he tried to

00:25:47.900 --> 00:25:49.590 line:80%
seize your family's property—

00:25:49.590 --> 00:25:50.910 line:80%
even a small county office

00:25:50.910 --> 00:25:52.390 line:80%
is full of intrigue.

00:25:52.790 --> 00:25:53.750 line:80%
Higher up—

00:25:54.070 --> 00:25:55.830 line:80%
in the prefecture and the court—

00:25:55.830 --> 00:25:58.490 line:80%
the web of relations
becomes even more tangled.

00:25:59.070 --> 00:26:02.170 line:80%
Factions, colleagues, mentors
and students, and family ties—

00:26:02.170 --> 00:26:03.770 line:80%
the officialdom of Great Yin

00:26:04.410 --> 00:26:06.540 line:80%
is bound together like a spider's web.

00:26:06.550 --> 00:26:08.070 line:80%
But what does my parents' death

00:26:08.070 --> 00:26:11.000 line:80%
have to do with the government
or the imperial court?

00:26:13.680 --> 00:26:15.280 line:80%
I was only giving an example.

00:26:19.440 --> 00:26:21.590 line:80%
No matter how vast the Great Yin court is,

00:26:21.590 --> 00:26:22.450 line:80%
it simply means

00:26:22.880 --> 00:26:24.940 line:80%
there are more officials with power.

00:26:25.720 --> 00:26:27.050 line:80%
If it comes to the worst,

00:26:27.390 --> 00:26:30.280 line:80%
I'll take my grievance
all the way to the Emperor.

00:26:31.280 --> 00:26:32.590 line:80%
No matter

00:26:32.720 --> 00:26:34.550 line:80%
who is involved in my parents' death,

00:26:34.550 --> 00:26:36.210 line:80%
I will investigate to the end.

00:26:36.390 --> 00:26:38.680 line:80%
I don't care about Great Yin's spiderweb.

00:26:38.680 --> 00:26:40.200 line:80%
They must follow state laws
and social rules.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:41.910 line:80%
There must be reason and justice.

00:26:41.910 --> 00:26:44.390 line:80%
Otherwise, the world
would fall into chaos.

00:26:48.870 --> 00:26:50.200 line:80%
If I were a man,

00:26:51.150 --> 00:26:53.390 line:80%
I might take the imperial examinations
or the military examinations

00:26:53.390 --> 00:26:54.590 line:80%
to enter officialdom

00:26:54.590 --> 00:26:57.120 line:80%
and get to the bottom
of my parents' deaths.

00:27:00.870 --> 00:27:02.240 line:80%
But I'm only a woman.

00:27:04.040 --> 00:27:05.570 line:80%
I can't become an official,

00:27:05.590 --> 00:27:07.590 line:80%
nor do I know any high-ranking ones.

00:27:09.070 --> 00:27:10.520 line:80%
The only way...

00:27:13.500 --> 00:27:15.570 line:80%
is to let money do the talking.

00:27:19.910 --> 00:27:22.000 line:80%
But the money needed
to move those high officials

00:27:22.000 --> 00:27:23.390 line:80%
won't be a small amount.

00:27:24.590 --> 00:27:25.870 line:80%
Every obstacle can be overcome;

00:27:25.870 --> 00:27:27.330 line:80%
there will always be a way.

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.400 line:80%
I've been meaning to ask—

00:27:34.550 --> 00:27:37.080 line:80%
is there anything you want
for your birthday?

00:27:39.110 --> 00:27:41.570 line:80%
I'm not in the mood
to celebrate my birthday.

00:27:42.410 --> 00:27:43.590 line:80%
Just make a wish.

00:27:44.160 --> 00:27:45.090 line:80%
Think of it as...

00:27:50.140 --> 00:27:52.940 line:80%
Think of it as a gift
for all your birthdays to come.

00:27:54.890 --> 00:27:55.940 line:80%
You're leaving?

00:28:04.780 --> 00:28:08.180 line:80%
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

00:28:07.140 --> 00:28:08.470 line:80%
Do you really have to go?

00:28:08.610 --> 00:28:11.430 line:80%
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

00:28:12.060 --> 00:28:15.270 line:80%
♪ For a chance encounter  ♪

00:28:16.510 --> 00:28:20.080 line:80%
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

00:28:19.040 --> 00:28:20.240 line:80%
Listen to me,

00:28:20.590 --> 00:28:22.760 line:80%
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

00:28:21.200 --> 00:28:23.190 line:80%
it's not like you're leaving forever.

00:28:23.190 --> 00:28:26.650 line:80%
♪ Just for a glance ♪

00:28:27.020 --> 00:28:27.780 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:28:27.800 --> 00:28:30.190 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:28:30.210 --> 00:28:32.000 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:28:30.850 --> 00:28:31.640 line:80%
Right?

00:28:32.450 --> 00:28:33.300 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:28:33.330 --> 00:28:36.230 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:28:36.260 --> 00:28:38.190 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:28:38.220 --> 00:28:38.860 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:42.040 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:28:42.080 --> 00:28:44.190 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

00:28:44.220 --> 00:28:48.900 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:28:49.670 --> 00:28:52.580 line:80%
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

00:28:55.640 --> 00:28:58.620 line:80%
[Li's Mansion]

00:28:57.410 --> 00:29:01.340 line:80%
My engagement to the Princess Royal is,
for now, agreed upon as stated.

00:29:09.760 --> 00:29:11.520 line:80%
Since Her Highness has said so,

00:29:11.520 --> 00:29:13.450 line:80%
this marriage is set.

00:29:13.520 --> 00:29:16.720 line:80%
What does it matter
if the wedding is delayed by two years?

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:21.880 line:80%
I thought you would be angry, Grandfather,

00:29:21.890 --> 00:29:24.420 line:80%
since the wedding
won't happen immediately.

00:29:24.760 --> 00:29:26.380 line:80%
Following your sister's appointment
as royal consort,

00:29:26.380 --> 00:29:28.830 line:80%
the Princess Royal is willing to
marry into our Li family.

00:29:28.830 --> 00:29:32.400 line:80%
Our clan shall once again
shine with honor.

00:29:32.550 --> 00:29:34.200 line:80%
My wish in this life

00:29:34.230 --> 00:29:35.710 line:80%
is now fulfilled!

00:29:39.070 --> 00:29:39.680 line:80%
By the way,

00:29:40.800 --> 00:29:43.660 line:80%
this urgent dispatch arrived today,
sent express.

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:45.210 line:80%
Take a look.

00:29:57.410 --> 00:29:59.270 line:80%
Wei Xuan has detained General He?

00:30:05.760 --> 00:30:07.360 line:80%
Please forgive my rudeness.

00:30:07.970 --> 00:30:09.660 line:80%
General He is a loyal and capable general

00:30:09.660 --> 00:30:10.790 line:80%
and also my teacher.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:13.310 line:80%
Seeing him persecuted like this,

00:30:13.310 --> 00:30:14.710 line:80%
I cannot just sit idly by.

00:30:17.520 --> 00:30:18.520 line:80%
So,

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:20.870 line:80%
you leave tonight.

00:30:20.870 --> 00:30:23.240 line:80%
Go back and assist He Jingyuan.

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:24.700 line:80%
And while you're at it,

00:30:25.040 --> 00:30:26.640 line:80%
hinder Wei Xuan.

00:30:27.680 --> 00:30:30.880 line:80%
Grandfather, do you not mind
that he's of the Wei faction?

00:30:31.550 --> 00:30:32.590 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:30:33.520 --> 00:30:34.590 line:80%
do you know

00:30:34.830 --> 00:30:37.720 line:80%
how turbulent the Imperial Court's
situation is at this moment?

00:30:37.720 --> 00:30:39.250 line:80%
Your teacher, He Jingyuan,

00:30:39.480 --> 00:30:42.660 line:80%
is a loyal and righteous general.

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:45.760 line:80%
He submits to Wei Yan solely
for the sake of the Imperial Court

00:30:45.760 --> 00:30:47.440 line:80%
and the people.

00:30:47.440 --> 00:30:50.550 line:80%
But it was because of Wei Yan's
groundless suspicion

00:30:50.960 --> 00:30:54.760 line:80%
that he ended up in prison.

00:30:54.910 --> 00:30:56.240 line:80%
You mean, Grandfather,

00:30:56.720 --> 00:30:58.720 line:80%
Wei Yan letting Wei Xuan act this way

00:30:58.800 --> 00:31:00.460 line:80%
is to isolate loyal subjects?

00:31:02.590 --> 00:31:03.550 line:80%
Back then,

00:31:04.310 --> 00:31:06.910 line:80%
Wei Yan and I both served
the Eastern Palace.

00:31:07.550 --> 00:31:09.310 line:80%
We once swore solemnly

00:31:09.630 --> 00:31:12.080 line:80%
to protect the realm of Great Yin.

00:31:12.440 --> 00:31:15.150 line:80%
But now, he's become a powerful minister,

00:31:15.550 --> 00:31:18.550 line:80%
monopolizing the court
and eliminating dissidents.

00:31:18.630 --> 00:31:19.760 line:80%
Our Li family

00:31:19.870 --> 00:31:22.800 line:80%
has naturally become a thorn in his side.

00:31:24.480 --> 00:31:25.590 line:80%
I know

00:31:26.070 --> 00:31:27.830 line:80%
you're like your teacher—

00:31:27.830 --> 00:31:31.200 line:80%
you care for the common people
and aim to protect them.

00:31:31.590 --> 00:31:33.550 line:80%
To realize your ideals,

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:35.960 line:80%
there is only one way.

00:31:36.870 --> 00:31:37.960 line:80%
That is

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:42.170 line:80%
to thoroughly eradicate
the treacherous officials led by Wei Yan.

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:44.770 line:80%
Only then can the chaos in the court
be quelled

00:31:44.830 --> 00:31:47.520 line:80%
and the foundation of the state secured.

00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:52.070 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:31:53.550 --> 00:31:55.390 line:80%
you're a good child.

00:31:55.390 --> 00:31:56.590 line:80%
Your sense of loyalty

00:31:56.960 --> 00:31:58.490 line:80%
is your greatest strength,

00:31:58.720 --> 00:32:02.270 line:80%
but it's also your weakness.

00:32:04.350 --> 00:32:07.630 line:80%
It is I who have burdened you.

00:32:11.350 --> 00:32:12.860 line:80%
I do this willingly.

00:32:12.980 --> 00:32:14.280 line:80%
I'll do everything in my power

00:32:14.280 --> 00:32:16.810 line:80%
to help you bring down Wei Yan
once and for all.

00:32:22.070 --> 00:32:25.000 line:80%
Reports from the front say our
Northwest Army is retreating in defeat.

00:32:25.000 --> 00:32:27.410 line:80%
The Eldest Young Master has even
imprisoned He Jingyuan.

00:32:27.410 --> 00:32:28.480 line:80%
He refuses to follow military orders

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:30.330 line:80%
or return to the capital with his troops.

00:32:30.330 --> 00:32:33.480 line:80%
He says, "A general in the field is not
bound by every command from above."

00:32:33.480 --> 00:32:34.680 line:80%
He wants to regroup

00:32:35.280 --> 00:32:36.210 line:80%
and fight again.

00:32:36.390 --> 00:32:37.390 line:80%
Fight again?

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:43.200 line:80%
The army is defeated and exhausted.
How can they fight again?

00:32:43.200 --> 00:32:44.110 line:80%
Moreover,

00:32:44.520 --> 00:32:46.150 line:80%
it's the middle of winter,
and the New Year has just passed.

00:32:46.150 --> 00:32:48.550 line:80%
Where would there even be
a battle to fight?

00:32:53.040 --> 00:32:53.760 line:80%
You,

00:32:53.870 --> 00:32:55.000 line:80%
take my commander's seal

00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:58.380 line:80%
and force him to hand over
military authority and He Jingyuan.

00:32:58.380 --> 00:32:59.300 line:80%
Then,

00:33:00.350 --> 00:33:02.210 line:80%
tie him up and bring him back to me.

00:33:03.350 --> 00:33:04.170 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:33:23.760 --> 00:33:24.560 line:80%
Grandfather,

00:33:25.350 --> 00:33:28.110 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an, Xie Zheng,
was set up during the battle in Chongzhou.

00:33:28.110 --> 00:33:29.720 line:80%
I have reliable information

00:33:29.740 --> 00:33:32.020 line:80%
that he's still alive.

00:33:32.680 --> 00:33:33.910 line:80%
I believe

00:33:34.100 --> 00:33:36.830 line:80%
if we can join forces
with the Marquis of Wu'an...

00:33:37.200 --> 00:33:39.460 line:80%
He's different from Prime Minister Wei.

00:33:40.690 --> 00:33:43.960 line:80%
Even if the uncle and nephew
have fallen out as rumored,

00:33:43.960 --> 00:33:46.530 line:80%
blood is still thicker than water.

00:33:46.960 --> 00:33:48.260 line:80%
Do not mention

00:33:48.680 --> 00:33:51.680 line:80%
allying with the Marquis of Wu'an
in front of me again.

00:34:08.439 --> 00:34:09.870 line:80%
Spread out and check
if anyone is still alive.

00:34:09.870 --> 00:34:10.680 line:80%
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:34:16.680 --> 00:34:18.740 line:80%
It was Wei Xuan's troops who did this.

00:34:19.830 --> 00:34:21.320 line:80%
Such wanton slaughter—

00:34:22.200 --> 00:34:23.800 line:80%
it's absolutely monstrous.

00:34:25.430 --> 00:34:26.510 line:80%
It wasn't Wei Xuan.

00:34:27.160 --> 00:34:29.689 line:80%
I've had men tracking
his troops' movements.

00:34:30.310 --> 00:34:33.840 line:80%
I'm afraid another group is
stirring the pot behind the scenes.

00:34:34.560 --> 00:34:36.200 line:80%
Quick, send word to Lord He.

00:34:36.200 --> 00:34:36.800 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:34:57.430 --> 00:34:58.510 line:80%
My Lord, look.

00:34:59.280 --> 00:35:00.310 line:80%
There're footprints.

00:35:00.310 --> 00:35:01.390 line:80%
Someone escaped.

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:04.820 line:80%
Could they have let one go on purpose?

00:35:06.910 --> 00:35:08.730 line:80%
Murder... Murder...

00:35:09.030 --> 00:35:11.080 line:80%
Murder... Murder! Murder!

00:35:11.470 --> 00:35:13.760 line:80%
Everyone, our Ma Village is poor.

00:35:14.240 --> 00:35:16.030 line:80%
We could barely pay the grain and taxes,

00:35:16.030 --> 00:35:18.830 line:80%
so our Community Head took us
to the county office to petition,

00:35:18.830 --> 00:35:20.590 line:80%
hoping for a chance to survive.

00:35:21.310 --> 00:35:22.470 line:80%
But who could've predicted

00:35:22.470 --> 00:35:26.870 line:80%
that halfway there, we'd be ambushed
and cut down by the county's own soldiers?

00:35:33.800 --> 00:35:36.440 line:80%
I only survived by playing dead!

00:35:38.240 --> 00:35:39.160 line:80%
Fellow villagers,

00:35:39.160 --> 00:35:41.720 line:80%
we should gather everyone in the village

00:35:41.720 --> 00:35:43.990 line:80%
and go with me to find
the damned corrupt official

00:35:43.990 --> 00:35:45.160 line:80%
to get justice

00:35:45.160 --> 00:35:46.390 line:80%
and take back our grain!

00:35:46.390 --> 00:35:47.350 line:80%
-Take back our grain!
-Take back our grain!

00:35:47.350 --> 00:35:49.160 line:80%
-We want justice!
-We want justice!

00:35:49.160 --> 00:35:50.030 line:80%
Kill that corrupt official!

00:35:50.030 --> 00:35:50.800 line:80%
-Kill that corrupt official!
-Kill that corrupt official!

00:35:50.800 --> 00:35:52.000 line:80%
Take back our grain!

00:35:52.030 --> 00:35:54.430 line:80%
-Take back our grain!
-Take back our grain!

00:36:03.120 --> 00:36:03.690 line:80%
General.

00:36:03.720 --> 00:36:04.650 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:36:04.760 --> 00:36:08.050 line:80%
General, the Wei Army has slaughtered
those innocent villagers.

00:36:08.050 --> 00:36:10.870 line:80%
Looks like Lord Changxin
has made his move.

00:36:10.900 --> 00:36:16.620 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:36:16.340 --> 00:36:19.570 line:80%
A perfectly healthy person,
dead just like that!

00:36:19.690 --> 00:36:20.470 line:80%
We can't let this go!

00:36:20.470 --> 00:36:21.020 line:80%
Exactly!

00:36:21.040 --> 00:36:22.500 line:80%
She must pay with her life!

00:36:23.860 --> 00:36:28.130 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:36:26.350 --> 00:36:27.760 line:80%
He died from their food!

00:36:27.780 --> 00:36:29.310 line:80%
A man died just like that?

00:36:32.310 --> 00:36:34.340 line:80%
Sir, what happened?

00:36:34.360 --> 00:36:35.530 line:80%
You don't know?

00:36:35.640 --> 00:36:37.800 line:80%
A man has died
after eating at Yixiang Restaurant!

00:36:37.800 --> 00:36:40.350 line:80%
His family came early this morning
to seek justice!

00:36:40.350 --> 00:36:42.680 line:80%
This Yixiang Restaurant is
nothing but a criminal den!

00:36:42.680 --> 00:36:43.490 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:36:43.510 --> 00:36:45.430 line:80%
that woman manager should
be arrested and beheaded!

00:36:45.430 --> 00:36:45.950 line:80%
Right!

00:36:45.970 --> 00:36:47.560 line:80%
A life for a life!

00:36:47.560 --> 00:36:48.910 line:80%
Don't you all agree?

00:36:48.910 --> 00:36:49.910 line:80%
-Yes!
-Exactly!

00:36:50.390 --> 00:36:51.490 line:80%
A life for a life!

00:36:51.720 --> 00:36:53.160 line:80%
They charge such high prices,

00:36:53.160 --> 00:36:54.430 line:80%
and they poison the food on top of it!

00:36:54.430 --> 00:36:56.310 line:80%
Yesterday, a customer suddenly fell ill
in the restaurant.

00:36:56.310 --> 00:36:58.600 line:80%
The manager noticed
and thought it might be epilepsy,

00:36:58.600 --> 00:37:00.270 line:80%
so she immediately sent someone
to fetch a doctor.

00:37:00.270 --> 00:37:02.760 line:80%
The customer's family
was very grateful at first.

00:37:02.760 --> 00:37:04.360 line:80%
But after they took him home,

00:37:04.430 --> 00:37:06.090 line:80%
he died suddenly in the night.

00:37:06.350 --> 00:37:07.510 line:80%
Early this morning,

00:37:07.510 --> 00:37:09.640 line:80%
they brought a coffin to the door
and made a scene,

00:37:09.640 --> 00:37:11.680 line:80%
demanding we pay for the old man's death.

00:37:11.680 --> 00:37:13.310 line:80%
Isn't that outright extortion?

00:37:13.310 --> 00:37:14.240 line:80%
-Yes.
-Exactly.

00:37:15.310 --> 00:37:16.570 line:80%
What did Qianqian say?

00:37:17.120 --> 00:37:18.870 line:80%
Our manager tried to reason with them

00:37:18.870 --> 00:37:19.950 line:80%
and offered money

00:37:19.950 --> 00:37:21.880 line:80%
to send those troublemakers away.

00:37:21.910 --> 00:37:24.830 line:80%
But those scoundrels refused
no matter what we offered.

00:37:24.830 --> 00:37:26.560 line:80%
They're clearly here to cause trouble.

00:37:26.560 --> 00:37:28.160 line:80%
The manager got suspicious,

00:37:28.160 --> 00:37:30.280 line:80%
fearing another restaurant
had set this up,

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:31.600 line:80%
so she went to report it to the officials.

00:37:31.600 --> 00:37:33.800 line:80%
But it's been a long time now,

00:37:33.800 --> 00:37:35.120 line:80%
and she hasn't come back yet.

00:37:35.120 --> 00:37:36.510 line:80%
This is so worrying!

00:37:36.510 --> 00:37:37.750 line:80%
-Yeah.
-Yes.

00:37:38.510 --> 00:37:40.200 line:80%
Someone is clearly scheming against you.

00:37:40.200 --> 00:37:41.800 line:80%
What should we do now?

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:43.240 line:80%
We can't just keep waiting here
and do nothing.

00:37:43.240 --> 00:37:43.830 line:80%
Well...

00:37:46.510 --> 00:37:47.350 line:80%
I have an idea.

00:37:47.640 --> 00:37:51.370 line:80%
But you'll have to lure the
police runners away from the door first.

00:37:54.510 --> 00:37:56.200 line:80%
That's so wicked!

00:38:01.230 --> 00:38:02.290 line:80%
See them?

00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:03.990 line:80%
Those three who talk the most.

00:38:03.990 --> 00:38:05.110 line:80%
The one with stubble.

00:38:05.110 --> 00:38:06.240 line:80%
The one with the hat.

00:38:06.780 --> 00:38:07.940 line:80%
And the one in black?

00:38:14.240 --> 00:38:16.450 line:80%
I'm never coming to the restaurant again!

00:38:16.450 --> 00:38:17.430 line:80%
Never again!

00:38:17.830 --> 00:38:19.690 line:80%
They must give us an explanation!

00:38:19.960 --> 00:38:23.580 line:80%
[Decheng's Tavern]

00:38:20.220 --> 00:38:21.880 line:80%
I heard long ago
that the manager of Yixiang Restaurant

00:38:21.880 --> 00:38:23.080 line:80%
knows some shady tricks.

00:38:23.080 --> 00:38:23.760 line:80%
Do it!

00:38:24.930 --> 00:38:25.990 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:38:28.080 --> 00:38:30.410 line:80%
Repaying debts is a universal principle!

00:38:30.550 --> 00:38:32.040 line:80%
Never seen a gambling house beat someone?

00:38:32.040 --> 00:38:33.180 line:80%
Never seen debt collectors at work?

00:38:32.250 --> 00:38:34.390 line:80%
[Decheng's Tavern]

00:38:33.350 --> 00:38:35.120 line:80%
What are you looking at? Get lost!

00:38:35.120 --> 00:38:35.870 line:80%
Get lost!

00:38:38.310 --> 00:38:39.160 line:80%
Take it away!

00:38:45.000 --> 00:38:46.130 line:80%
Behave yourselves.

00:39:03.350 --> 00:39:04.120 line:80%
Speak.

00:39:05.050 --> 00:39:07.980 line:80%
Who sent you to cause trouble
at Yixiang Restaurant?

00:39:11.830 --> 00:39:13.510 line:80%
No one sent us.

00:39:13.850 --> 00:39:16.470 line:80%
Someone died from the food here.

00:39:16.500 --> 00:39:18.600 line:80%
Are we not allowed to seek justice?

00:39:18.620 --> 00:39:20.240 line:80%
You've tied us up and brought us here.

00:39:20.240 --> 00:39:21.370 line:80%
Do you want to kill us

00:39:21.390 --> 00:39:23.950 line:80%
to silence everyone?

00:39:24.160 --> 00:39:26.510 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant is no restaurant.

00:39:26.510 --> 00:39:28.950 line:80%
It's clearly a murderous den of thieves!

00:39:28.950 --> 00:39:29.910 line:80%
-Exactly!
-Exactly!

00:39:29.910 --> 00:39:31.570 line:80%
It's clearly a criminal den!

00:39:36.420 --> 00:39:37.870 line:80%
You talk too much.

00:39:41.720 --> 00:39:43.780 line:80%
That tongue of yours is quite nimble.

00:39:45.240 --> 00:39:47.200 line:80%
Cut it out, chop it up,
and feed it to the dogs.

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:47.870 line:80%
No.

00:39:48.390 --> 00:39:50.640 line:80%
Heroine, that's against the law!

00:39:51.030 --> 00:39:51.510 line:80%
Heroine!

00:39:51.510 --> 00:39:52.280 line:80%
Wait, wait!

00:39:54.200 --> 00:39:55.110 line:80%
I mean it!

00:39:55.680 --> 00:39:56.740 line:80%
Spare me, Heroine!

00:39:57.430 --> 00:39:58.200 line:80%
Of course!

00:40:10.640 --> 00:40:12.570 line:80%
That fellow struggled quite a bit.

00:40:12.870 --> 00:40:14.870 line:80%
I couldn't get the whole tongue out,

00:40:14.910 --> 00:40:16.910 line:80%
so I only managed to chop off a piece.

00:40:17.220 --> 00:40:19.620 line:80%
This pig's tongue looks quite convincing.

00:40:20.120 --> 00:40:21.050 line:80%
Bring a dog here.

00:40:22.160 --> 00:40:23.960 line:80%
Take it out and feed it to the dog.

00:40:44.200 --> 00:40:44.910 line:80%
Speak.

00:40:45.240 --> 00:40:47.170 line:80%
Who sent you here to cause trouble?

00:40:47.440 --> 00:40:48.880 line:80%
If you utter a single lie,

00:40:49.430 --> 00:40:52.470 line:80%
your tongues will also be cut out
and fed to the dog.

00:40:53.200 --> 00:40:53.830 line:80%
I'll talk. I'll talk.

00:40:53.830 --> 00:40:54.800 line:80%
I'll tell you! I'll tell you!

00:40:54.800 --> 00:40:55.910 line:80%
-I'll go first!
-I'll go first.

00:40:55.910 --> 00:40:57.350 line:80%
-Me first!
-I'll go first!

00:40:57.350 --> 00:40:58.560 line:80%
-Me!
-Me!

00:40:58.560 --> 00:40:59.380 line:80%
Enough!

00:41:00.680 --> 00:41:01.310 line:80%
You speak.

00:41:01.350 --> 00:41:02.280 line:80%
It was Advisor Guo...

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:04.840 line:80%
It was Advisor Guo's page boy who sent us.

00:41:09.870 --> 00:41:10.800 line:80%
You're lying!

00:41:10.950 --> 00:41:13.470 line:80%
Milady, we really aren't lying!

00:41:13.470 --> 00:41:16.130 line:80%
It really was Advisor Guo's page boy
who sent us!

00:41:18.350 --> 00:41:21.120 line:80%
Advisor Guo has no grudge against
Yixiang Restaurant.

00:41:21.120 --> 00:41:22.720 line:80%
Why would he make you do this?

00:41:22.990 --> 00:41:24.080 line:80%
We don't know either.

00:41:24.080 --> 00:41:25.470 line:80%
Still not telling the truth, huh?

00:41:25.470 --> 00:41:26.350 line:80%
Someone come here!

00:41:26.350 --> 00:41:27.800 line:80%
Cut off their tongues
and feed them to the dog!

00:41:27.800 --> 00:41:28.830 line:80%
-We really don't know!
-We really don't know!

00:41:28.830 --> 00:41:30.640 line:80%
We don't know! We really don't know!

00:41:30.640 --> 00:41:31.600 line:80%
We really don't know!

00:41:31.600 --> 00:41:32.760 line:80%
Let them go.

00:41:40.200 --> 00:41:43.060 line:80%
Aren't you taking them to court
for confrontation?

00:41:43.390 --> 00:41:45.310 line:80%
You just got it out of them yourself.

00:41:45.310 --> 00:41:47.970 line:80%
It was Advisor Guo
who instructed those people.

00:41:49.680 --> 00:41:51.830 line:80%
Some restaurant trying to
steal your business

00:41:51.830 --> 00:41:53.490 line:80%
found their way to Advisor Guo

00:41:53.640 --> 00:41:55.030 line:80%
and tried to frame you?

00:41:57.280 --> 00:41:58.720 line:80%
It's even worse than that.

00:41:58.720 --> 00:42:00.380 line:80%
Then what exactly is going on?

00:42:03.950 --> 00:42:06.150 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant is about to be lost.

00:42:06.370 --> 00:42:07.390 line:80%
I was out all morning,

00:42:07.390 --> 00:42:08.720 line:80%
calling in every favor I could—

00:42:08.720 --> 00:42:11.050 line:80%
but I didn't get to see
a single one of them.

00:42:11.140 --> 00:42:14.210 line:80%
Even Magistrate Cui avoided me.

00:42:19.390 --> 00:42:21.310 line:80%
My family has some connections
with Constable Wang at the county office.

00:42:21.310 --> 00:42:22.240 line:80%
I'll go speak with him

00:42:22.240 --> 00:42:23.720 line:80%
and see if he can help you.

00:42:23.720 --> 00:42:24.680 line:80%
It's useless.

00:42:26.510 --> 00:42:28.110 line:80%
I appreciate your kindness.

00:42:28.390 --> 00:42:30.120 line:80%
Don't go to
Constable Wang for help either,

00:42:30.120 --> 00:42:31.650 line:80%
lest you bring him trouble.

00:42:34.120 --> 00:42:35.240 line:80%
Manager, bad news!

00:42:35.350 --> 00:42:37.600 line:80%
Police runners have forced their way in
through the back door.

00:42:37.600 --> 00:42:38.600 line:80%
I'll go there now.

00:42:39.120 --> 00:42:39.870 line:80%
I'll go take a look too.

00:42:39.870 --> 00:42:40.910 line:80%
I want to know who exactly they are

00:42:40.910 --> 00:42:42.840 line:80%
and what they're trying to do here.

00:42:42.870 --> 00:42:43.830 line:80%
Don't stick your neck out for me.

00:42:43.830 --> 00:42:45.960 line:80%
You'll only end up caught in a lawsuit.

00:42:46.080 --> 00:42:47.870 line:80%
I know Magistrate Cui very well.

00:42:47.870 --> 00:42:49.640 line:80%
I have my own way of handling this.

00:42:49.640 --> 00:42:51.240 line:80%
What's more important now is

00:42:51.430 --> 00:42:52.470 line:80%
that you stay here

00:42:52.830 --> 00:42:54.690 line:80%
and make sure no one finds Bao'er.

00:43:02.720 --> 00:43:05.050 line:80%
You're Manager Yu of Yixiang Restaurant?

00:43:05.080 --> 00:43:05.720 line:80%
I am.

00:43:06.470 --> 00:43:07.270 line:80%
Take her away!

00:43:09.680 --> 00:43:10.240 line:80%
Okay.

00:43:10.730 --> 00:43:12.200 line:80%
I'll come with you to the county office.